HEADWORD: Sea adder
<hw>Sea" ad"der</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <sd>(a)</sd>
<def>The European fifteen-spined stickleback (<spn>Gasterosteus
spinachia</spn>); -- called also <altname>bismore</altname>.</def>
<sd>(b)</sd> <def>The European tanglefish, or pipefish (<spn>Syngnathus
acus</spn>).</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Sea anchor</ent>⟦br⟧
